FBIS4-39464 "drsov110_a_94041" FBIS-SOV-94-110 Daily Report 7 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Gas Firm Breaks From Ukraine, Merges With Gazprom Gas Firm Breaks From Ukraine, Merges With Gazprom MK0706133094 Moscow SEGODNYA in Russian 7 Jun 94 p 2 MK0706133094 Moscow SEGODNYA Russian BFN [Unattributed report: "YuzhNIIGiprogaz Intends To Affiliate With RAO Gazprom] [Text] The Donetsk-based YuzhNIIGiprogaz has moved away from the jurisdiction of the Ukraine State Oil and Gas Committee and intends to become an affiliated enterprise of RAO Gazprom. This was announced by the Russian Fuel and Energy Ministry. In the event that YuzhNIIGiprogaz becomes part of the RAO, a precedent will be set for corporatizing Ukraine's gas industry enterprises as part of Gazprom.
